### **3. 25_LogEchoAnalyzer**  
**Description:**  
Scans and analyzes logs to surface repeated or suspicious entries.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogEchoAnalyzer - Repetition and Error Pattern Scanner

LogEchoAnalyzer detects noisy or repeating lines in logs and helps identify the most common system issues.

## Features
- Frequency sorting  
- Works on rotated and large logs  
- Filter by keywords  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_LogEchoAnalyzer.git
cd 25_LogEchoAnalyzer
python analyze.py logs/app.log
